  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/95104bab4e0c6a4239d443cd0fd24865.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through unique arcade style challenges that will test your aim in all aspects. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Standard training modes will perfect all your skills from accuracy and speed to tracking and flicking. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Scoring System will reward good habits. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Rating System for completed challenges assigns a rating based on your performance. Everyone wants to see that Diamond rating. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards displaying the best Aimers and their score in each game mode. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements are ready to be collected at every corner.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/d0176c9e3826db97ddddd173aa84a422.poster.avif?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/d0176c9e3826db97ddddd173aa84a422.webm?t=1749156502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Aim Expert is a skill based aiming simulator providing arcade style levels and standard aim training modes. Challenge yourself in all aspects of aiming and climb the leaderboards to showcase your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/c71d7533a7df02b17035f2981e660e24.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a challenging journey that will test but also sharpen your aiming skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/59fbc90306aa2096649b42aa9bf1c915.poster.avif?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/59fbc90306aa2096649b42aa9bf1c915.webm?t=1749156502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/07f0ed9a13f6634a32fceceab80d4e0e.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win or fail, it doesn't matter. Regular exercise of an activity or skill is the way to become proficient in it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/8783a7e2719a46acb3fb0de48bab9c7c.poster.avif?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/8783a7e2719a46acb3fb0de48bab9c7c.webm?t=1749156502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're looking to have fun, trying to get a high score or take your aim to the next level, Aim Expert has something for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/bf90a17bb0e4a7b91596f1cbbca7c1f1.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/95104bab4e0c6a4239d443cd0fd24865.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through unique arcade style challenges that will test your aim in all aspects. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Standard training modes will perfect all your skills from accuracy and speed to tracking and flicking. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Scoring System will reward good habits. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Rating System for completed challenges assigns a rating based on your performance. Everyone wants to see that Diamond rating. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards displaying the best Aimers and their score in each game mode. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements are ready to be collected at every corner.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/d0176c9e3826db97ddddd173aa84a422.poster.avif?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/d0176c9e3826db97ddddd173aa84a422.webm?t=1749156502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Aim Expert is a skill based aiming simulator providing arcade style levels and standard aim training modes. Challenge yourself in all aspects of aiming and climb the leaderboards to showcase your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/c71d7533a7df02b17035f2981e660e24.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a challenging journey that will test but also sharpen your aiming skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/59fbc90306aa2096649b42aa9bf1c915.poster.avif?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/59fbc90306aa2096649b42aa9bf1c915.webm?t=1749156502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/07f0ed9a13f6634a32fceceab80d4e0e.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win or fail, it doesn't matter. Regular exercise of an activity or skill is the way to become proficient in it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/8783a7e2719a46acb3fb0de48bab9c7c.poster.avif?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/8783a7e2719a46acb3fb0de48bab9c7c.webm?t=1749156502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're looking to have fun, trying to get a high score or take your aim to the next level, Aim Expert has something for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214030/extras/bf90a17bb0e4a7b91596f1cbbca7c1f1.webp?t=1749156502\" width=650 height=30 /></span></p>",
